    <para>Notes utilisateur&nbsp;: <ulink url="&hlfs-wiki;/gcc"/></para>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de GCC Libssp</title>

    <para>La bibliothèque <filename class="libraryfile">libssp</filename> est
		utilisée pour FIXME.</para>

    <para>Préparez la compilation de Libssp&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir -v libssp/build
cd libssp/build
env CC="gcc -nointl -fno-stack-protector -U_FORTIFY_SOURCE" \
    ../configure --prefix=/usr</userinput></screen>

    <para>Compilez le paquet&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Installez Libssp&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>make install
rm -v /usr/lib/libssp.so
mv -v /usr/lib/libssp.so.* /lib
ln -vsf ../../lib/libssp.so.0 /usr/lib/libssp.so</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

